123
00:05:44,890 --> 00:05:46,560
on others to poop and pee.

124
00:05:46,730 --> 00:05:47,900
More importantly,

125
00:05:48,040 --> 00:05:50,650
this won't bring him back to life.

126
00:05:51,390 --> 00:05:53,230
