127
00:05:53,430 --> 00:05:54,590
he's already dead.

128
00:05:57,159 --> 00:05:58,630
Are you two still willing to be my representatives?

129
00:05:59,480 --> 00:06:00,630
If not,

130
00:06:01,100 --> 00:06:02,050
I can find someone else.

131
00:06:04,120 --> 00:06:04,950
Ms. Li.

132
00:06:06,120 --> 00:06:08,030
If you choose to give up now,

133
00:06:08,750 --> 00:06:10,010
will you be okay with that?

134
00:06:11,630 --> 00:06:12,920
Will you have the feeling

135
00:06:13,160 --> 00:06:14,920
of betraying your past relationship?

136
00:06:16,160 --> 00:06:17,040
Do you think I'm doing all these things

137
00:06:17,040 --> 00:06:18,360
just for myself?

138
00:06:21,310 --> 00:06:23,430
Let me tell you something about Yuan Gang and me.

139
00:06:24,560 --> 00:06:25,120
Once,

140
00:06:25,120 --> 00:06:26,920
we went to climb a snowy mountain abroad.

141
00:06:27,250 --> 00:06:29,100
Unexpectedly, we encountered a blizzard on the mountain

142
00:06:30,120 --> 00:06:31,680
and had to spend the night there.

143
00:06:32,630 --> 00:06:34,680
Although we weren't novices in outdoor activities,

144
00:06:35,270 --> 00:06:36,510
on that day, we both felt that

145
00:06:36,510 --> 00:06:37,830
we were surely going to die.

146
00:06:38,490 --> 00:06:39,850
At that moment, I asked Yuan Gang,

147
00:06:40,680 --> 00:06:42,800
"We're always pushing our limits

148
00:06:43,360 --> 00:06:45,000
and risking our lives like this.

149
00:06:45,000 --> 00:06:45,680
Do you think it's worth it?"

150
00:06:46,720 --> 00:06:48,830
Yuan Gang said if he could live again,

151
00:06:49,720 --> 00:06:51,430
he would make the same choices.

152
00:06:53,120 --> 00:06:54,690
At that time, we made a promise to each other.

153
00:06:55,680 --> 00:06:57,430
If both of us could survive back then,

154
00:06:58,310 --> 00:06:59,680
and if one day in the future,

155
00:07:00,170 --> 00:07:02,120
we should encounter today's situation,

156
00:07:03,480 --> 00:07:05,360
one of us would have to take responsibility for the other,

157
00:07:07,480 --> 00:07:10,480
and when it's time to give up, we should give up.

158
00:07:12,300 --> 00:07:14,370
I know this is a tough choice,

159
00:07:15,500 --> 00:07:16,730
and I'll have to bear it for a lifetime.

160
00:07:17,710 --> 00:07:19,080
But I'm willing to bear the consequences.

161
00:07:20,180 --> 00:07:21,630
I have to let him pass away with dignity.

162
00:07:23,120 --> 00:07:24,030
Ms. Li.

163
00:07:25,310 --> 00:07:26,780
You are truly remarkable.

164
00:07:31,600 --> 00:07:32,640
Don't worry.

165
00:07:33,120 --> 00:07:34,270
We've decided that

166
00:07:34,870 --> 00:07:36,390
we will represent your case.

167
00:07:36,830 --> 00:07:38,480
And we will do our best

168
00:07:38,480 --> 00:07:40,190
to help you win this lawsuit.

169
00:07:40,800 --> 00:07:43,800
We hope to fulfill Mr. Yuan Gang's wishes.

170
00:07:46,040 --> 00:07:46,630
Thank you.

171
00:07:48,430 --> 00:07:49,390
Thank you, ladies.

172
00:07:51,240 --> 00:07:52,240
