223
00:09:34,870 --> 00:09:36,200
But you haven't noticed that behind this,

224
00:09:36,200 --> 00:09:37,790
there is also joy for me.

225
00:09:38,750 --> 00:09:39,840
Yuan Gang's father

226
00:09:39,840 --> 00:09:41,980
passed away when he was 12 years old.

227
00:09:42,120 --> 00:09:43,040
After that,

228
00:09:43,200 --> 00:09:45,240
we lived together.

229
00:09:45,910 --> 00:09:47,550
I was a teacher by profession.

230
00:09:47,960 --> 00:09:51,360
I'm well aware that as a single mother who raises a son,

231
00:09:51,360 --> 00:09:53,320
it's necessary to cultivate his independent personality.

232
00:09:53,630 --> 00:09:56,270
So, as soon as he got into university,

233
00:09:56,270 --> 00:09:58,150
I asked him to move out and live alone

234
00:09:58,350 --> 00:09:59,510
so that he could face the society

235
00:09:59,550 --> 00:10:01,030
and deal with difficulties and challenges by himself.

236
00:10:01,390 --> 00:10:03,510
He was quite capable.

237
00:10:04,180 --> 00:10:05,610
As he knew that life wasn't easy for me,

238
00:10:06,390 --> 00:10:09,030
when he had the opportunity to study abroad later,

239
00:10:09,030 --> 00:10:10,790
he didn't go, and he just gave up.

240
00:10:11,270 --> 00:10:12,600
After they got married,

241
00:10:12,720 --> 00:10:14,320
they bought a small house for me

242
00:10:14,360 --> 00:10:15,880
right next to their new house

243
00:10:16,120 --> 00:10:17,790
so that when he was free,

244
00:10:18,030 --> 00:10:19,590
he could often come to visit me.

245
00:10:22,960 --> 00:10:23,810
I'm just thinking that

246
00:10:24,670 --> 00:10:26,630
after such a serious accident,

247
00:10:26,750 --> 00:10:29,870
the reason why he's not willing to give up on his own life

248
00:10:30,670 --> 00:10:34,030
might be that he's worried about me.

249
00:10:35,150 --> 00:10:37,120
He can't bear to let me

250
00:10:37,150 --> 00:10:40,120
live alone in this world.

251
00:10:40,140 --> 00:10:40,900
Ms. Cui,

252
00:10:41,080 --> 00:10:41,870
we've also

253
00:10:41,870 --> 00:10:44,030
learned some information indirectly.

254
00:10:45,630 --> 00:10:46,840
As husband and wife,

255
00:10:46,840 --> 00:10:47,960
Li Yuan and Yuan Gang

256
00:10:47,960 --> 00:10:49,390
might have made some agreements before.

257
00:10:49,390 --> 00:10:51,780
For example, if such a situation occurs,

258
00:10:52,360 --> 00:10:54,550
they'll be willing to give up active treatment

259
00:10:55,320 --> 00:10:58,320
to end their lives.

260
00:10:58,790 --> 00:10:59,950
I don't believe it.

261
00:11:01,200 --> 00:11:03,460
Yuan Gang has never said such things to me.

262
00:11:04,390 --> 00:11:06,610
But there is one thing I know.

263
00:11:08,000 --> 00:11:09,160
Because of scuba diving,

264
00:11:09,510 --> 00:11:10,720
they both

265
