Thank you.

838
00:34:46,090 --> 00:34:47,420
You're welcome. It's our duty.

839
00:35:02,840 --> 00:35:04,110
They're coming.

840
00:35:08,000 --> 00:35:10,160
Ms. Luo, what's your view on today's verdict?

841
00:35:10,840 --> 00:35:13,030
We're disappointed at the outcome of the verdict.

842
00:35:14,470 --> 00:35:15,630
With the advancement of times,

843
00:35:15,950 --> 00:35:17,950
people's views on life and death should change, too.

844
00:35:18,260 --> 00:35:20,220
When a person exists merely as a physical body,

845
00:35:20,420 --> 00:35:22,820
maintaining his life without dignity is meaningless.

846
00:35:23,050 --> 00:35:25,050
We understand the applicant's

847
00:35:25,240 --> 00:35:26,240
request in this case.

848
00:35:26,670 --> 00:35:27,720
However, we don't think that

849
00:35:28,040 --> 00:35:29,600
she should use her personal emotions

850
00:35:29,630 --> 00:35:31,240
to control others and the deceased.

851
00:35:31,410 --> 00:35:32,850
Do you plan to appeal?

852
00:35:33,150 --> 00:35:34,590
We've discussed it with our client.

853
00:35:34,900 --> 00:35:35,970
We won't appeal.

854
00:35:36,200 --> 00:35:36,760
However,

855
00:35:37,190 --> 00:35:37,960
it doesn't mean that

856
00:35:37,960 --> 00:35:39,710
we agree with the verdict.

857
00:35:39,730 --> 00:35:41,250
Thank you. Excuse me.

858
00:35:41,760 --> 00:35:42,710
Thank you, Mr. Chen.

859
00:35:42,730 --> 00:35:45,080
There's no need to thank me. It's my duty.

860
00:35:46,430 --> 00:35:47,350
You don't need to worry now.

861
00:35:49,030 --> 00:35:49,510
Ms. Cui,

862
00:35:49,510 --> 00:35:51,840
the court has designated you as Yuan Gang's guardian.

863
00:35:51,840 --> 00:35:52,550
Is there anything you want to say?

864
00:35:52,580 --> 00:35:53,390
You guys can leave first.

865
00:35:53,470 --> 00:35:54,990
My son is not dead.

866
00:35:55,700 --> 00:35:56,970
As long as I'm alive,

867
00:35:57,240 --> 00:35:58,360
he won't die.

868
00:35:58,430 --> 00:36:00,030
He will stay alive with me forever.

869
00:36:00,760 --> 00:36:03,320
I'm grateful for the court's fair judgment.

870
00:36:03,590 --> 00:36:05,030
Mr. Chen, your statement in court

871
00:36:05,030 --> 00:36:05,760
was very powerful.

872
00:36:05,760 --> 00:36:06,280
I wonder

873
00:36:06,280 --> 00:36:08,130
in your opinion, what the significance of this case is.

874
00:36:12,190 --> 00:36:13,230
I...

875
00:36:16,190 --> 00:36:17,440
Or do you have anything else to say

876
00:36:17,440 --> 00:36:18,760
about this verdict?

877
00:36:20,920 --> 00:36:22,360
I'm sorry, but we have no comment.

878
00:36:22,360 --> 00:36:23,190
Come on. Excuse me. Please make way.

879
00:36:23,190 --> 00:36:23,870
Thank you.

880
00:36:23,900 --> 00:36:24,970
Excuse me.

881
00:36:25,300 --> 00:36:27,220
Mr. Chen, just get back to work.

882
00:36:27,250 --> 00:36:28,410
I need to go to the hospital now.

883
00:36:29,280 --> 00:36:29,960
Please go ahead.

884
00:36:29,960 --> 00:36:30,360
Alright.

885
00:36:30,360 --> 00:36:31,150
Ms. Cui, let's keep in touch.

886
00:36:31,150 --> 00:36:31,550
Okay.

887
00:36:31,550 --> 00:36:32,840
Alright. Fang Rui, please escort Ms. Cui.

888
00:36:32,840 --> 00:36:33,390
-Okay.
-Thank you.

889
00:36:33,410 --> 00:36:33,890
Take care.

890
00:36:33,920 --> 00:36:34,360
Goodbye.

891
00:36:34,380 --> 00:36:35,200
Come on. This way, please.

892
00:36:38,950 --> 00:36:40,950
I told you not to take this case.

893
00:36:41,560 --> 00:36:42,530
It has hurt your relationship with her so much.

894
00:36:50,480 --> 00:36:51,230
Mentor.

895
00:36:52,760 --> 00:36:53,590
Go after her now!

896
00:36:53,820 --> 00:36:55,490
Work is work, and life is life.

897
00:36:56,150 --> 00:36:57,190
Don't mix them up.

898
00:36:58,130 --> 00:36:58,780
I won't go after her.

899
00:36:59,000 --> 00:37:00,190
Luo Yingzi has never lost before.

900
00:37:00,210 --> 00:37:01,300
Since she has lost this time,

901
00:37:01,430 --> 00:37:03,070
I have to give her some time to cure her wounds.

902
00:37:03,480 --> 00:37:04,220
Let's not think about it anymore.

903
00:37:04,250 --> 00:37:05,640
We won, didn't we? Let's go have a meal.

904
00:37:05,660 --> 00:37:06,150
Drive the car.

905
00:37:08,150 --> 00:37:08,810
Let's go.

906
00:38:39,320 --> 00:38:39,860
Dad.

907
00:38:41,130 --> 00:38:41,960
I'm back.

908
00:38:43,840 --> 00:38:44,510
Yingzi.

909
00:38:45,280 --> 00:38:46,360
Why are you back?

910
00:38:46,920 --> 00:38:48,760
I've received the calligraphy work you sent me.

911
00:38:48,850 --> 00:38:50,400
I just want to come back to see you.

912
00:38:51,840 --> 00:38:53,110
Is everything alright?

913
00:38:53,830 --> 00:38:55,100
What could be wrong with me?

914
00:38:55,510 --> 00:38:56,360
Just go on sitting here.

915
00:38:56,440 --> 00:38:57,760
I'll put my things in the room.

916
00:39:02,710 --> 00:39:04,480
Dad, dinner's ready. Let's eat.

917
00:39:05,170 --> 00:39:05,780
Yingzi.

918
00:39:06,220 --> 00:39:06,860
Come here.

919
00:39:08,920 --> 00:39:09,590
What's wrong?

920
00:39:11,000 --> 00:39:12,590
I'm not able to remove this hangnail

921
00:39:12,670 --> 00:39:13,670
on my finger.

922
00:39:14,640 --> 00:39:16,160
I'm long-sighted. Look.

923
00:39:17,690 --> 00:39:19,000
Help me cut it off.

924
00:39:20,500 --> 00:39:20,980
Dad.

925
00:39:21,350 --> 00:39:22,730
If your eyesight isn't good,

926
00:39:22,760 --> 00:39:23,630
just don't try to cut it yourself.

927
00:39:23,630 --> 00:39:24,840
Look. You've hurt your finger.

928
00:39:25,920 --> 00:39:26,590
Wait a moment.

929
00:39:26,590 --> 00:39:28,070
I'll get some ointment for you.

930
00:39:28,850 --> 00:39:30,040
Don't try to cut it now.

931
00:39:33,190 --> 00:39:36,110
Chen Shuo is such a lucky man.

932
00:39:36,850 --> 00:39:38,640
He has my good daughter as his girlfriend.

933
00:39:39,770 --> 00:39:40,930
He's truly blessed.

934
00:39:42,300 --> 00:39:43,010
Look.

935
00:39:43,280 --> 00:39:43,780
Dad.

936
00:39:45,530 --> 00:39:47,010
You're trying to get information out of me, aren't you?

937
00:39:49,810 --> 00:39:51,650
Can I get any information out of you?

938
00:39:52,120 --> 00:39:53,330
You won't get any information out of me.

939
00:39:55,290 --> 00:39:56,810
Bear the pain. It might hurt a bit.

940
00:39:57,360 --> 00:39:58,150
Bear the pain.

941
00:39:58,670 --> 00:39:59,360
Okay.

942
00:40:01,300 --> 00:40:01,820
Dad.

943
00:40:02,570 --> 00:40:03,770
Are you missing my mom?

944
00:40:04,570 --> 00:40:05,880
How can you say that?

945
00:40:09,210 --> 00:40:11,730
From the moment I walked in until just now,

946
00:40:11,760 --> 00:40:13,470
I noticed that you kept looking at this hand.

947
00:40:14,960 --> 00:40:15,920
Did you

948
00:40:17,030 --> 00:40:19,060
regret signing it for my mother back then?

949
00:40:21,790 --> 00:40:23,190
I've never regretted it.

950
00:40:24,190 --> 00:40:25,550
But at that time,

951
00:40:26,430 --> 00:40:28,030
if we had kept her alive just like that,

952
00:40:28,630 --> 00:40:29,360
what if

953
00:40:29,830 --> 00:40:31,060
she could wake up one day?

954
00:40:33,950 --> 00:40:34,950
As for this question,

955
00:40:35,700 --> 00:40:38,130
your mother and I discussed it many times.

956
00:40:39,380 --> 00:40:40,780
We both agreed that

957
00:40:41,180 --> 00:40:44,230
we should live well while we are alive,

958
00:40:44,680 --> 00:40:45,950
and once our bodies can't function anymore,

959
00:40:46,260 --> 00:40:48,220
we should leave this world without hesitation,

960
00:40:49,950 --> 00:40:51,840
lest we should become a burden to you.

961
00:40:51,870 --> 00:40:53,270
Dad, how can you say that?

962
00:40:54,030 --> 00:40:56,360
How could you two possibly be a burden to me?

963
00:40:58,480 --> 00:40:59,040
Yingzi.

964
00:41:00,130 --> 00:41:02,530
Let's agree on this first.

965
00:41:02,990 --> 00:41:05,510
Once my body can't function anymore,

966
00:41:05,840 --> 00:41:07,880
just let me pass away without hesitation.

967
00:41:11,220 --> 00:41:12,740
But before I pass away,

968
00:41:13,760 --> 00:41:15,280
I just hope to see that

969
00:41:15,960 --> 00:41:17,190
someone loves you

970
00:41:17,690 --> 00:41:18,850
and you have a family.

971
00:41:22,350 --> 00:41:25,190
Is Chen Shuo that person?

972
00:41:26,380 --> 00:41:26,870
Dad,

973
00:41:27,620 --> 00:41:29,190
do you really want to meet him?

974
00:41:30,630 --> 00:41:32,470
Actually, I haven't let you meet him

975
00:41:32,500 --> 00:41:35,230
because I was afraid you wouldn't like him.

976
00:41:38,010 --> 00:41:40,930
It doesn't matter whether I like him or not.

977
00:41:41,720 --> 00:41:44,680
What's important is whether you like him or not.

978
00:41:46,570 --> 00:41:49,260
I'm not the one who will marry him. Right?

979
00:41:49,880 --> 00:41:50,380
Alright.

980
00:41:51,080 --> 00:41:52,500
I'll bring him over next time

981
00:41:52,710 --> 00:41:53,660
so that you can meet him.

982
00:41:54,000 --> 00:41:54,690
The sooner, the better.

983
00:41:54,720 --> 00:41:55,240
Okay.

984
00:41:55,530 --> 00:41:56,620
Come on. Let's go have dinner.

985
00:41:56,810 --> 00:41:58,770
Don't let this hand get wet for the time being.

986
00:41:58,800 --> 00:41:59,430
Okay.

987
00:42:00,600 --> 00:42:01,360
After dinner,

988
00:42:01,380 --> 00:42:02,370
I'll trim your nails for you.

989
00:42:09,820 --> 00:42:11,640
[Righteous Luo]

990
00:42:16,840 --> 00:42:17,710
Righteous Luo.

991
00:42:18,760 --> 00:42:20,710
You turned around and walked away outside the court that day.

992
00:42:20,710 --> 00:42:21,760
I thought you would be ignoring me.

993
00:42:22,120 --> 00:42:24,250
I've been waiting for your call so eagerly.

994
00:42:24,590 --> 00:42:25,630
Stop it.

995
00:42:25,890 --> 00:42:27,400
I just went back to my hometown.

996
00:42:27,400 --> 00:42:29,600
And when I came back, no one was there to pick me up.

997
00:42:30,280 --> 00:42:31,840
I even had to go back by myself.

998
00:42:32,190 --> 00:42:33,630
You went home and wanted me to pick you up.

999
00:42:33,630 --> 00:42:35,030
But you didn't tell me.

1000
00:42:35,190 --> 00:42:35,760
Besides,

1001
00:42:35,760 --> 00:42:37,150
why didn't you take me with you when you went home?

1002
00:42:37,250 --> 00:42:38,770
Why didn't you let me meet my future father-in-law?

1003
00:42:39,190 --> 00:42:40,590
Don't be so shameless.

1004
00:42:41,420 --> 00:42:42,780
It's still up in the air.

1005
00:42:43,900 --> 00:42:45,700
Well, are you free?

1006
00:42:45,900 --> 00:42:47,220
Shall we meet now?

1007
00:42:47,530 --> 00:42:48,780
What? Are you going to get even with me?

1008
00:42:49,150 --> 00:42:50,320
That's pretty much what I mean.

1009
00:42:50,590 --> 00:42:51,840
I want to review things with you.

1010
00:42:51,840 --> 00:42:52,920
It's about that case.

1011
00:42:53,530 --> 00:42:55,300
What do you think? Is it okay?

1012
00:42:55,920 --> 00:42:56,880
Do you want to meet me now?

1013
00:42:56,880 --> 00:42:58,000
Are you free today?

1014
00:42:58,440 --> 00:42:59,070
Yes, I am.

1015
00:42:59,320 --> 00:43:00,280
Do you need me to pick you up?

1016
00:43:00,550 --> 00:43:01,110
No need.

1017
00:43:01,110 --> 00:43:02,480
I've already called a car.

